Учим переводить деньги в Россию

> Sending funds to Russia can be a nightmare for the treasury department.
Mistakes in the large list of details requested by the Russian Central Bank
are a usual cause of payment reversals that cause disruptions to companies’
cash flows. In this article, we want to let you know which details are
mandatory to fulfil and where to get them, as a good number of them should be
provided to you by the Russian beneficiary.  
Additionally, we will advise you of other details that are not mandatory but
would be highly recommendable to include to assure that the payment is
received.  
_In order to make your life easier, we have grouped the list of requirements in three main categories._  
—  [How to send money transfers to Russia and not die trying](https://www.kantox.com/en/send-money-transfers-russia-not-die-trying/?utm_content=56220546&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter).

